Homepage: https://github.com/Sanona-Ltd/froxlor-DEV
Description: Froxlor - Web Hosting Control Panel
 Froxlor is a lightweight open-source web hosting control panel
 built on Laravel 12 with Tailwind CSS and Alpine.js.
 .
 Features:
  - Clean admin dashboard and customer panel
  - Domain management with per-domain webserver selection
    (Apache, Nginx, OpenLiteSpeed)
  - Built-in WAF with Cloudflare-style JS challenge protection
  - IP blacklist, CIDR blocks and User-Agent filtering
